    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>PizzaExpress</strong> <strong>pizza dough</strong> in half</p><p>Shape the<strong> dough </strong>into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> balls and set aside for 15 min</p>",
